Installation Instructions
-------------------------

Requires Python 2.6 or higher.

On Windows, download the .zip archive from here: http://github.com/marksweiss/organize-m/downloads. Unzip into any directory you desire, and run Organize-m from there.  

On Mac or Linux, download the .tar archive from here: http://github.com/marksweiss/organize-m/downloads. Untar into any directory you desire and run Organize-m from there.

For full documentation of the command line interface, see the README here: http://github.com/marksweiss/organize-m
